g-o-o-o away ♪

15:41.290 --> 15:42.960
What's Asher saying?

15:42.960 --> 15:45.460
They're almost here.

15:45.460 --> 15:47.330
Go. You can meet them.
I can do this solo.

15:48.500 --> 15:51.000
♪ G-o-o-o away ♪

15:51.000 --> 15:52.460
What's wrong with you,
Marcus?

15:52.460 --> 15:54.250
Huh?

15:54.250 --> 15:55.540
Are you an egomaniac?

15:55.540 --> 15:58.210
Do you wear sock with sandals?
Or is it a micropenis?

15:58.210 --> 16:02.580
Because it makes no sense
why you don't have someone.

16:04.500 --> 16:07.960
Or maybe you do and
you just haven't told me.

16:07.960 --> 16:11.830
♪ Smarter, stronger ♪

16:11.830 --> 16:12.880
♪ Mm-mmm ♪

16:12.880 --> 16:15.710
There was someone,

16:15.710 --> 16:18.210
but she had a chance to do
something great without me.

16:18.210 --> 16:21.880
And I couldn't
hold her back from that.

16:21.880 --> 16:23.920
♪ Make it through ♪

16:23.920 --> 16:26.460
♪ What is to do ♪

16:26.460 --> 16:28.120
♪ Now out the way ♪

16:28.120 --> 16:30.000
I hate you so much.

16:30.000 --> 16:31.420
♪ You could try
and numb the pain ♪

16:31.420 --> 16:37.420
♪ But it'll never
g-o-o-o away ♪

16:37.960 --> 16:40.250
♪ You could try
and numb the pain ♪

16:40.250 --> 16:44.290
♪ But it'll never
g-o-o-o away ♪

16:52.580 --> 16:56.210
[ Gil Scott-Heron's
"Me and the Devil" plays ]

16:56.210 --> 17:02.250
♪♪

17:05.250 --> 17:08.170
Nate: The guards will bring
you in before court starts.

17:08.170 --> 17:10.620
It'll be crowded --
full gallery.

17:10.620 --> 17:13.380
Plus all the Justices
and the clerks and...

17:13.380 --> 17:15.170
You say that like you think
I'm gonna flip out in there.

17:15.170 --> 17:17.000
I just want you
to be prepared.

17:17.000 --> 17:20.250
I've sit quiet for 30 years.
I got this.

17:20.250 --> 17:22.960
Okay.

17:22.960 --> 17:24.670
No good?

17:26.540 --> 17:28.290
♪ Early this morning ♪

17:31.420 --> 17:33.920
♪ When you knocked
